31:57.190 --> 31:58.230
Adakah semuanya diubah?

32:07.750 --> 32:08.120
Siapa?

32:11.610 --> 32:12.170
Bunyi apa?

32:17.630 --> 32:18.640
Rasanya

32:19.160 --> 32:20.830
